graph LR
A[Run-of-Mine (ROM) Ore] --> B{Jaw Crusher/Gyratory Crusher}
B --> C{Crushed Ore}
C --> D{SAG Mill/Ball Mill}
D --> E{Slurry}
E --> F{Flotation Cell}
    F {Collectors (attach to Cu & Au)}
    F {Frothers (create air bubbles)}
    F {Modifiers (control pH & interactions)}
F --> G{Air}
F --> H{Hydrophobic Cu & Au (to Froth)}
F --> I{Hydrophilic Waste (to Pulp)}
H --> J{Copper-Gold Concentrate}
J --> K{Ball Mill (regrind)}
K --> L{Copper Concentrate}
I --> M{Tailings}
M --> N{Tailings Storage Facility (TSF)}
L --> O{Transport & Smelting}
